774
00:55:30,400 --> 00:55:31,840
Yeah, I know. I was just...

775
00:55:32,010 --> 00:55:34,440
I mean, why can't you
just leave me alone?

776
00:55:46,420 --> 00:55:48,780
What are ya doing?I don't know.

777
00:55:49,200 --> 00:55:50,640
