792
00:57:06,410 --> 00:57:08,850
You were lovely.
About me, anyways.

793
00:57:09,020 --> 00:57:12,020
Of course I was lovely about you.

794
00:57:12,200 --> 00:57:14,360
What else is there to be about ya?

795
00:58:19,740 --> 00:58:21,593
What was that? A bird?

796
00:58:22,010 --> 00:58:23,400
What was what?

797
00:58:23,570 --> 00:58:24,960
The bang at the door.

798
00:58:25,010 --> 00:58:26,050
