804
00:58:35,410 --> 00:58:36,410
hard to lie...

805
00:58:36,590 --> 00:58:38,890
it was, uh...

806
00:58:39,070 --> 00:58:41,420
a finger.

807
00:58:45,420 --> 00:58:46,380
