813
00:59:01,870 --> 00:59:03,140
Shoebox.

814
00:59:03,440 --> 00:59:05,440
Oh, my. Oh, God.

815
00:59:05,620 --> 00:59:06,310
Well,

816
00:59:07,880 --> 00:59:08,790
he's serious, then.

817
01:00:26,220 --> 01:00:28,060
