827
01:00:55,250 --> 01:00:57,160
Well, what are we going to do?

828
01:00:57,340 --> 01:00:59,080
We can't keep a man's finger.

829
01:01:25,580 --> 01:01:27,190
Jesus, Colm!

830
01:01:28,720 --> 01:01:30,500
Did it hurt?

831
01:01:30,670 --> 01:01:34,353
Hurt awful to begin with.
Thought I was going to faint.

832
01:01:34,980 --> 01:01:38,250
It's funny, feels fine now,
