from Lisdoonvarna.

875
01:06:09,080 --> 01:06:10,520
Yeah, a telegram came for ya.

876
01:06:10,820 --> 01:06:12,520
From your mammy.

877
01:06:12,690 --> 01:06:14,350
My mammy is no longer with us.

878
01:06:14,520 --> 01:06:16,480
Not your mammy, sorry.

879
01:06:16,660 --> 01:06:18,513
Did I say your mammy?
Your auntie. Yeah, your auntie.

880
01:06:18,530 --> 01:06:20,140
It's about your daddy.

881
01:06:20,310 --> 01:06:21,790
