892
01:06:48,640 --> 01:06:51,170
If it's the same fecking
bread van, I'll kill them.

893
01:07:08,050 --> 01:07:08,750
Thanks.

894
01:07:11,360 --> 01:07:13,433
What were you talking to the boat fella for?

895
01:07:13,450 --> 01:07:16,160
For none of your fecking
business, I think it was.

896
01:07:16,190 --> 01:07:18,100
