for that battering I owe him.

901
01:07:25,200 --> 01:07:26,680
A battering?

902
01:07:26,860 --> 01:07:29,673
That'd be good, actually.
It might take him out of himself.

903
01:07:29,753 --> 01:07:30,860
Huh?

904
01:07:31,030 --> 01:07:33,080
You're an awful strange lady.

905
01:07:33,910 --> 01:07:36,133
No wonder no one likes ya.

906
01:08:03,630 --> 01:08:04,890
Oh.

907
01:08:05,070 --> 01:08:06,590
Hello there, Mrs. McCormick.

908
01:08:06,770 --> 01:08:10,940
A death shall come to Inisherin
afore the month is out.

909
01:08:11,510 --> 01:08:13,030
A death, huh?

910
01:08:13,210 --> 01:08:15,560
Maybe even two deaths.

911
01:08:16,640 --> 01:08:17,650
Well, that'd be sad.

912
01:08:19,560 --> 01:08:21,650
We shall pray to the Lord

913
01:08:21,820 --> 01:08:26,130
'tis neither you, nor poor Siobhan,
will be either of them.

914
01:08:26,310 --> 01:08:28,220
Well, is that a nice thing to be sayin'?

915
01:08:28,400 --> 01:08:30,220
I wasn't trying to be nice.

916
01:08:31,490 --> 01:08:33,490
I was trying to be accurate.

917
01:08:37,970 --> 01:08:39,230
Fecking hell.

918
01:09:12,000 --> 01:09:13,440
What's the matter?

919
01:09:15,440 --> 01:09:16,530
Nothing.

920
01:09:51,390 --> 01:09:52,880
Me daddy say he's gonna kill you Sunday

921
01:09:52,960 --> 01:09:55,933
for spilling the beans
about that fiddling with me.

922
01:09:59,660 --> 01:10:01,400
"Kill me," kill me, or, you know,

923
01:10:01,580 --> 01:10:04,060
"beat me up a bit," kill me?

924
01:10:04,230 --> 01:10:06,710
"Beat you up a bit," kill ya, I think.

925
01:10:06,890 --> 01:10:08,500
Although he did kill a man once.

926
01:10:13,020 --> 01:10:15,986
I'm sorry for that spilling
the beans on ya, Dominic.

927
01:10:16,070 --> 01:10:18,110
I was out of order that night.

928
01:10:18,420 --> 01:10:20,810
You was funny apart from that bit.

929
01:10:20,990 --> 01:10:24,160
That's why I don't understand why
that fat fella threw the finger at ya.

930
01:10:24,210 --> 01:10:25,573
He seemed fine when you were slagging him.

931
01:10:25,600 --> 01:10:27,380
He did not.

932
01:10:27,560 --> 01:10:29,080
Did he?

933
01:10:29,390 --> 01:10:32,706
