ever want to, I don't know,

986
01:13:44,490 --> 01:13:46,980
to fall in love with a boy
like me, would ya?

987
01:13:49,540 --> 01:13:52,280
Oh, Dominic, I don't think so, love.

988
01:13:52,460 --> 01:13:55,110
No, yeah, no.
Uh, I was thinking no.

989
01:13:58,290 --> 01:14:01,860
Not even in the future, like?
Like when I'm your age?

990
01:14:08,560 --> 01:14:11,960
Yeah, no, I didn't think so.

991
01:14:12,130 --> 01:14:14,520
Just thought I'd ask
on the off chance, you know,

992
01:14:14,700 --> 01:14:16,350
like, "faint heart" and that.

993
01:14:22,360 --> 01:14:23,880
Well, there goes that dream.

994
01:14:30,320 --> 01:14:32,110
Well,

995
01:14:32,280 --> 01:14:36,766
