1013
01:15:48,490 --> 01:15:51,050
That's right. The epitome!

1014
01:15:51,230 --> 01:15:54,060
Heh. There'll be none of that!
I didn't come here for licks!

1015
01:15:54,106 --> 01:15:55,386
